@startuml
title UC-12 Modify Course (Sequence)
participant Instructor
participant WebApp
participant CourseService
participant DB
participant NotificationService
participant Admin

Instructor -> WebApp: edit course content -> submit
WebApp -> CourseService: updateCourse(courseId, changes)
CourseService -> DB: validate & UPDATE course
DB --> CourseService: updated
alt changes require reapproval
CourseService -> DB: set status = PENDING_REVIEW
CourseService -> NotificationService: notifyAdmins(courseId)
NotificationService -> Admin: notify
end
CourseService -> NotificationService: notifyEnrolledIfNeeded(courseId, changes)
CourseService --> WebApp: ack
WebApp --> Instructor: show updated status
@enduml
